void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xy = u_xlat16_1.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_43 = dot(vs_TEXCOORD3, vs_TEXCOORD3);
    u_xlat16_43 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_43);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_43) * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_43 = dot(vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz, vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_43 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_43);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_43) * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_43 = dot(vs_TEXCOORD5, vs_TEXCOORD5);
    u_xlat16_43 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_43);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_43) * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyw = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyw;
    u_xlat16_43 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_43 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_43);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_43) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_2.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat16_43 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_43 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_43);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_43) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_43) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_44 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_44 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_44);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_44) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_44 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_44 = min(max(u_xlat16_44, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_44 = clamp(u_xlat16_44, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat42 = texture(_FurLengthTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_5.x = texture(_NoiseTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.zw).x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb19 = !!(0.00999999978>=u_xlat42);
#else
    u_xlatb19 = 0.00999999978>=u_xlat42;
#endif
    u_xlat16_45 = (u_xlatb19) ? 1.0 : 0.0;
    u_xlat16_46 = (-u_xlat16_5.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat16_45 * u_xlat16_46 + u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_46 = u_xlat16_44 + (-_EdgeFade);
    u_xlat16_46 = u_xlat16_46 + 0.800190985;
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat16_45 * u_xlat16_46;
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat16_45 * _AlphaAdjust;
    u_xlat16_46 = u_xlat16_45 * 2.23713636;
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat16_45 * 2.23713636 + -0.0500000007;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb5 = !!(u_xlat16_45<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb5 = u_xlat16_45<0.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb5){discard;}
    u_xlat16_45 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_45 = min(max(u_xlat16_45, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_45 = clamp(u_xlat16_45, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_6 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat16_6.x + _MetallicOffset;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_18 = min(max(u_xlat16_18, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_18 = clamp(u_xlat16_18, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_32 = u_xlat16_6.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_32 = max(u_xlat16_32, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_32 = min(u_xlat16_32, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_32 * u_xlat16_32;
    u_xlat16_21 = log2(abs(u_xlat16_6.z));
    u_xlat16_21 = u_xlat16_21 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_21 = exp2(u_xlat16_21);
    u_xlat16_21 = min(u_xlat16_21, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_35.x = u_xlat16_6.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_35.x = u_xlat16_35.x * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_35.xxx;
    u_xlat16_35.x = (-u_xlat16_18) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_35.xxx;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_18) * u_xlat16_10.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat16_1.y * u_xlat16_1.y;
    u_xlat19 = u_xlat16_1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat5.z = u_xlat5.x * 0.125 + u_xlat19;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat19);
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat5.zx + vec2(0.125, 0.125);
    u_xlat16_35.xy = max(u_xlat6.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_35.xy = u_xlat16_35.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_35.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_35.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35.x = dot((-u_xlat16_3.xyz), u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35.x = u_xlat16_35.x + u_xlat16_35.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * (-u_xlat16_35.xxx) + (-u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35.x = (-u_xlat16_44) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_35.x * u_xlat16_35.x;
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_49 * u_xlat16_49;
    u_xlat16_50 = (-u_xlat16_32) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_32 * u_xlat16_50;
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_5 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_50);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_5.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = log2(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_3.x = exp2(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xxx;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_21) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xy = u_xlat16_7.xx * u_xlat16_7.xx + vec2(1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_50 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_50);
    u_xlat16_50 = (-u_xlat16_32) + 1.03999996;
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat16_18 * 0.959999979 + u_xlat16_50;
    u_xlat16_12.xzw = (-u_xlat16_10.xyz) + vec3(u_xlat16_18);
    u_xlat16_12.xzw = vec3(u_xlat16_49) * u_xlat16_12.xzw + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_21) * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xzw + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_12.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_7.x / u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat16_32 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_18 * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_45) * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = min(u_xlat16_12.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_45) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_45 = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_45 = min(max(u_xlat16_45, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_45 = clamp(u_xlat16_45, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_45) + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_45 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_45 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_45);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_45) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_45 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_45 = min(max(u_xlat16_45, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_45 = clamp(u_xlat16_45, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(u_xlat16_45);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightScale;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_43) + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_43 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);

    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat5.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlatb42 = _DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978;
    u_xlat16_1.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb42) ? -1.0 : u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat42 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat5.xy = vec2(u_xlat42) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat5.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat5.xy;
    u_xlat10_42 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat5.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(u_xlat16_15.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_1.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat10_42 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (-u_xlat16_1.x) + u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_15.x = log2(u_xlat16_44);
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat16_15.x = exp2(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-u_xlat16_15.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = (-_DigiBaseColor0.xyz) * u_xlat16_15.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_15.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    return;
}

    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_46 / u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat0.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_4.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_4.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_6.x * u_xlat16_4.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_22.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_20.xyz;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_20.xyz;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = max(u_xlat16_20.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = min(u_xlat16_20.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xyz * u_xlat16_18.xxx + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_1.x);
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_44) + u_xlat16_20.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat16_15.xyz, u_xlat16_20.xyz);
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_44 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_44 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_44);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_44) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(u_xlat16_15.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.x = (-u_xlat16_15.x) * u_xlat16_15.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat14 = u_xlat16_18.y * u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat14 * u_xlat14 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 0.00100000005);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_18.y / u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat28;
    u_xlat0.x = min(u_xlat0.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_23.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = log2(u_xlat16_1.x);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * _AddlightScale;
    u_xlat16_1.x = exp2(u_xlat16_1.x);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz * vec3(vec3(_AddlightLerp, _AddlightLerp, _AddlightLerp)) + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-_AddlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_6.x * u_xlat16_2.x + _AddlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = min(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * u_xlat16_18.xxx + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD6.yzw * u_xlat16_22.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat5.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = (-_DigiBaseColor0.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_45) + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_45) * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlatb0 = _DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978;
    u_xlat16_43 = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_43 = (u_xlatb0) ? -1.0 : u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_43 + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16_44 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_44 = min(u_xlat16_44, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_44 * u_xlat16_43 + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat10_0.x = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat10_0.x + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat16_43 = (-u_xlat16_43) + u_xlat16_44;
    u_xlat16_43 = clamp(u_xlat16_43, 0.0, 1.0);
    SV_Target0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_43) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    return;
}

void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = texture(_FurLengthTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb14 = !!(0.00999999978>=u_xlat0.x);
#else
    u_xlatb14 = 0.00999999978>=u_xlat0.x;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(u_xlat0.x>=0.00999999978);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat0.x>=0.00999999978;
#endif
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb14) ? 1.0 : 0.0;
    u_xlat16_14.x = texture(_NoiseTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.zw).x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-u_xlat16_14.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_15.x + u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz, vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(vs_TEXCOORD5, vs_TEXCOORD5);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_3.yyy;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat16_15.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(vs_TEXCOORD3, vs_TEXCOORD3);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_15.xyz, u_xlat16_15.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_2.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat16_44 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_44 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_44);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_44) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(u_xlat16_15.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_3.x + (-_EdgeFade);
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_17.x + 0.800190985;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * _AlphaAdjust;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_1.x * 2.23713636 + -0.0500000007;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * 2.23713636;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    SV_Target0.w = min(max(SV_Target0.w, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    SV_Target0.w = clamp(SV_Target0.w, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb14 = !!(u_xlat16_17.x<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb14 = u_xlat16_17.x<0.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb14){discard;}
    u_xlat14 = (-_SelfShadowStrength) * 0.552999973 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb0) ? u_xlat14 : 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_44) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_17.xyz, u_xlat16_17.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_17.x = dot(u_xlat16_15.xyz, u_xlat16_17.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_17.x = min(max(u_xlat16_17.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_17.x = clamp(u_xlat16_17.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_17.x * u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_0.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_31 = max(u_xlat16_31, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_31 = min(u_xlat16_31, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat16_31 * u_xlat16_31;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = vec2(u_xlat16_45) * vec2(u_xlat16_45) + vec2(1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_17.x * u_xlat16_4.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_45 / u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_17.x * u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat16_31 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_17.x * u_xlat16_18;
    u_xlat16_17.x = min(u_xlat16_17.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat16_18 = dot(u_xlat16_15.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_18 = min(max(u_xlat16_18, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_18 = clamp(u_xlat16_18, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_32 = u_xlat16_0.x + _MetallicOffset;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_32 = min(max(u_xlat16_32, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_32 = clamp(u_xlat16_32, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_32) * u_xlat16_6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_18) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xxx * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat8.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(vs_TEXCOORD7.xy,vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
    u_xlat16_0.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_0.x * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_17.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb14 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb14 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb14 || u_xlatb0;
    u_xlat16_17.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = min(u_xlat16_9.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_46 = (-u_xlat16_32) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_46) * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_18) * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat16_17.x + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_18 = min(max(u_xlat16_18, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_18 = clamp(u_xlat16_18, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_15.y * u_xlat16_15.y;
    u_xlat14 = u_xlat16_15.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat47 = u_xlat0.x * 0.125 + u_xlat14;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat14);
    u_xlat0.y = u_xlat0.x + 0.125;

    u_xlat16_23.xyz = u_xlat16_9.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_23.xyz;
    u_xlat16_46 = log2(abs(u_xlat16_0.z));

    u_xlat16_46 = min(u_xlat16_46, 1.0);

    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_48 = (-u_xlat16_31) + 1.03999996;

    u_xlat16_12.xyz = (-u_xlat16_6.xyz) + vec3(u_xlat16_32);
    u_xlat16_32 = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = log2(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat16_3.x = exp2(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_32 * u_xlat16_32;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_48 * u_xlat16_48;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_48) * u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;

    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_18) + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(_RimLightDir, _RimLightDir);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat16_15.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat14 = u_xlat16_31 + 1.0;
    u_xlat28 = u_xlat16_31 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat14 = u_xlat14 * u_xlat14;
    u_xlat42 = u_xlat14 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (-u_xlat14) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_32 * u_xlat16_1.x + u_xlat42;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_32 / u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat0.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_31 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_31 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_31;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_31;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_31;
    u_xlat16_31 = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_17.x * u_xlat16_31 + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_31;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_10.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_46) + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_1.x);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_44) + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat16_15.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_44 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_44 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_44);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_44) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(u_xlat16_15.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat0.x = (-u_xlat16_15.x) * u_xlat16_15.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat14 = u_xlat16_45 * u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat14 * u_xlat14 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 0.00100000005);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_45 / u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat28;
    u_xlat0.x = min(u_xlat0.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = log2(u_xlat16_1.x);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * _AddlightScale;
    u_xlat16_1.x = exp2(u_xlat16_1.x);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * vec3(vec3(_AddlightLerp, _AddlightLerp, _AddlightLerp)) + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-_AddlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_17.x * u_xlat16_2.x + _AddlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = min(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_46) + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD6.yzw * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat5.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);

    u_xlatb0 = !!(_DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978);

    u_xlatb0 = _DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978;
#endif
    u_xlat16_43 = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_43 = (u_xlatb0) ? -1.0 : u_xlat16_43;

    u_xlat16_44 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xy = u_xlat16_1.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_40 = dot(vs_TEXCOORD3, vs_TEXCOORD3);
    u_xlat16_40 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_40);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_40) * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_40 = dot(vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz, vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_40 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_40);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_40) * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_40 = dot(vs_TEXCOORD5, vs_TEXCOORD5);
    u_xlat16_40 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_40);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_40) * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyw = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyw;

uniform 	mediump float _FurLength;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _NoiseTex_ST;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerDraw {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightData;

	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_ProbesOcclusion;

#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(1) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTexMouth_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTexEye_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _FurTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _BumpMap_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _BaseColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Emissive;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SpecularColor;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiBaseColor1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiHighColor;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DigiPow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DigiDistore;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;

UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(8) uniform mediump sampler2D _FurLengthTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
float u_xlat18;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.zw = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _NoiseTex_ST.xy + _NoiseTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_FurLengthTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).x;
    u_xlat6.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(_FurLength);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.446999997, 0.446999997, 0.446999997) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = vec2(u_xlat18) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat1.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat18 = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat1.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(_DigiDistore);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * in_TANGENT0.www;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _NoiseTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(8) uniform mediump sampler2D _FurLengthTex;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
bool u_xlatb0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
bool u_xlatb5;
mediump float u_xlat16_6;
vec2 u_xlat7;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_12;
float u_xlat13;
uint u_xlatu13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_14;
mediump float u_xlat16_17;
float u_xlat18;
bool u_xlatb18;
mediump float u_xlat16_19;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_24;
float u_xlat26;
int u_xlati26;
bool u_xlatb26;
mediump float u_xlat16_30;
mediump float u_xlat16_32;
float u_xlat39;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
bool u_xlatb39;
mediump float u_xlat16_40;
mediump float u_xlat16_41;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
mediump float u_xlat16_43;
float u_xlat44;
mediump float u_xlat16_45;
mediump float u_xlat16_47;
mediump float u_xlat16_48;
mediump float u_xlat16_49;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xy = u_xlat16_1.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_40 = dot(vs_TEXCOORD3, vs_TEXCOORD3);
    u_xlat16_40 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_40);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_40) * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_40 = dot(vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz, vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_40 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_40);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_40) * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_40 = dot(vs_TEXCOORD5, vs_TEXCOORD5);
    u_xlat16_40 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_40);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_40) * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyw = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyw;
    u_xlat16_40 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_40 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_40);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_40) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(vs_TEXCOORD7.xy,vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
    u_xlat16_39 = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_40 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_40 = u_xlat16_39 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_40;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb39 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb39 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb5 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb5 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb39 = u_xlatb39 || u_xlatb5;
    u_xlat16_40 = (u_xlatb39) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_40;
    u_xlat16_2.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_2.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat16_41 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_41 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_41);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_41) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;

void main()
{

    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.446999997, 0.446999997, 0.446999997) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = vec2(u_xlat18) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat1.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat18 = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat1.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(_DigiDistore);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * in_TANGENT0.www;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;

in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;

vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
bool u_xlatb0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;

mediump vec3 u_xlat16_26;

int u_xlati30;
bool u_xlatb30;
mediump float u_xlat16_33;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
float u_xlat45;
mediump float u_xlat16_45;
bool u_xlatb45;
mediump float u_xlat16_46;
mediump float u_xlat16_47;
mediump float u_xlat16_48;

mediump float u_xlat16_51;

void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xy = u_xlat16_1.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_46 = dot(vs_TEXCOORD3, vs_TEXCOORD3);
    u_xlat16_46 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_46);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_46) * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_46 = dot(vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz, vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_46 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_46);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_46) * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_46 = dot(vs_TEXCOORD5, vs_TEXCOORD5);
    u_xlat16_46 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_46);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_46) * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyw = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyw;
    u_xlat16_46 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_46 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_46);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_46) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(vs_TEXCOORD7.xy,vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
    u_xlat16_45 = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_46 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_46 = u_xlat16_45 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_46;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb45 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb45 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb5 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb5 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb45 = u_xlatb45 || u_xlatb5;
    u_xlat16_46 = (u_xlatb45) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_46;
    u_xlat16_2.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_2.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat16_47 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_47 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_47);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_47) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_47) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_48 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_48 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_48);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_48) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat45 = texture(_FurLengthTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_5.x = texture(_NoiseTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.zw).x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb20 = !!(0.00999999978>=u_xlat45);
#else
    u_xlatb20 = 0.00999999978>=u_xlat45;
#endif
    u_xlat16_18.x = (u_xlatb20) ? 1.0 : 0.0;
    u_xlat16_33 = (-u_xlat16_5.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_33 + u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_3.x + (-_EdgeFade);
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_33 + 0.800190985;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_33 * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x * _AlphaAdjust;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_18.x * 2.23713636;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x * 2.23713636 + -0.0500000007;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb5 = !!(u_xlat16_18.x<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb5 = u_xlat16_18.x<0.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb5){discard;}
    u_xlat16_18.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_18.x = min(max(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_18.x = clamp(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_48 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_48 = min(max(u_xlat16_48, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_48 = clamp(u_xlat16_48, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_4 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_4.x + _MetallicOffset;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_6.x = min(max(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_6.x = clamp(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_21 = u_xlat16_4.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_21 = max(u_xlat16_21, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_21 = min(u_xlat16_21, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_21 * u_xlat16_21;
    u_xlat16_51 = log2(abs(u_xlat16_4.z));
    u_xlat16_51 = u_xlat16_51 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_51 = exp2(u_xlat16_51);
    u_xlat16_51 = min(u_xlat16_51, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_4.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xxx;
    u_xlat16_52 = (-u_xlat16_6.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_52);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat16_1.y * u_xlat16_1.y;
    u_xlat20 = u_xlat16_1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat5.z = u_xlat5.x * 0.125 + u_xlat20;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat20);
    u_xlat10.xy = u_xlat5.zx + vec2(0.125, 0.125);
    u_xlat16_11.xy = max(u_xlat10.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_11.xy = u_xlat16_11.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_26.xyz = u_xlat16_11.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_26.xyz;
    u_xlat16_52 = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_53 = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat16_53 = u_xlat16_53 * u_xlat16_53;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_51) * _GlossyEnvironmentColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xy = vec2(u_xlat16_36) * vec2(u_xlat16_36) + vec2(1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_54 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_54);
    u_xlat16_54 = (-u_xlat16_21) + 1.03999996;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x * 0.959999979 + u_xlat16_54;
    u_xlat16_13.xzw = (-u_xlat16_9.xyz) + u_xlat16_6.xxx;
    u_xlat16_13.xzw = vec3(u_xlat16_53) * u_xlat16_13.xzw + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_51) * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz;

    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_16.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;

  Name "ForwardLit"

  Tags { "IGNOREPROJECTOR" = "true" "LIGHTMODE" = "FurPass2" "QUEUE" = "Geometry" "RenderPipeline" = "LightweightPipeline" "RenderType" = "[_RenderType]" }

  GpuProgramID 182472
Program "vp" {
SubProgram "gles " {
Keywords { "_DEBUG_OFF" }

#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];

uniform 	mediump vec4 _NoiseTex_ST;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.zw = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _NoiseTex_ST.xy + _NoiseTex_ST.zw;

    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;

    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * in_TANGENT0.www;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);

    u_xlat10_0.x = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat10_0.x + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat16_40 = (-u_xlat16_40) + u_xlat16_41;
    u_xlat16_40 = clamp(u_xlat16_40, 0.0, 1.0);
    SV_Target0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_40) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    return;
}

vec4 u_xlat0;

mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
float u_xlat18;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.zw = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _NoiseTex_ST.xy + _NoiseTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_FurLengthTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).x;
    u_xlat6.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(_FurLength);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.632000029, 0.632000029, 0.632000029) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = vec2(u_xlat18) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat1.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat18 = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat1.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(_DigiDistore);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * in_TANGENT0.www;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);

    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;

UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _FurLengthTex;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
vec2 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
mediump float u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
float u_xlat13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
bool u_xlatb13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_14;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_17;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_19;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_21;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_22;
float u_xlat26;
float u_xlat39;
mediump float u_xlat16_40;
mediump float u_xlat16_41;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
mediump float u_xlat16_43;
mediump float u_xlat16_45;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = texture(_FurLengthTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb13 = !!(0.00999999978>=u_xlat0.x);
#else
    u_xlatb13 = 0.00999999978>=u_xlat0.x;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(u_xlat0.x>=0.00999999978);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat0.x>=0.00999999978;
#endif
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb13) ? 1.0 : 0.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = texture(_NoiseTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.zw).x;
    u_xlat16_14.x = (-u_xlat16_13.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_14.x + u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_14.x = dot(vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz, vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_14.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_14.x);
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(vs_TEXCOORD5, vs_TEXCOORD5);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_3.yyy;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat16_14.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(vs_TEXCOORD3, vs_TEXCOORD3);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_14.xyz, u_xlat16_14.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;

SubProgram "gles " {

#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];

uniform 	mediump vec4 _NoiseTex_ST;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;

vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.zw = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _NoiseTex_ST.xy + _NoiseTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = u_xlat0;

    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;

    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);

}

    u_xlat16_40 = (-u_xlat16_40) + u_xlat16_41;

    SV_Target0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_40) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    return;

void main()
{
    u_xlat0.zw = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _NoiseTex_ST.xy + _NoiseTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = u_xlat0;

    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.632000029, 0.632000029, 0.632000029) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = vec2(u_xlat18) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat1.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat18 = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat1.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(_DigiDistore);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + u_xlat0.xyz;

    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;

    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;

    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;

mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;

mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;

mediump vec3 u_xlat16_14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_16;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_17;
float u_xlat26;
mediump float u_xlat16_29;
mediump float u_xlat16_30;

mediump float u_xlat16_41;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
mediump float u_xlat16_43;
float u_xlat44;
mediump float u_xlat16_45;
mediump float u_xlat16_46;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = texture(_FurLengthTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb13 = !!(0.00999999978>=u_xlat0.x);
#else
    u_xlatb13 = 0.00999999978>=u_xlat0.x;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(u_xlat0.x>=0.00999999978);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat0.x>=0.00999999978;
#endif
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb13) ? 1.0 : 0.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = texture(_NoiseTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.zw).x;
    u_xlat16_14.x = (-u_xlat16_13.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_14.x + u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_14.x = dot(vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz, vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_14.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_14.x);
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(vs_TEXCOORD5, vs_TEXCOORD5);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_3.yyy;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat16_14.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(vs_TEXCOORD3, vs_TEXCOORD3);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_14.xyz, u_xlat16_14.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_2.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat16_41 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_41 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_41);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_41) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(u_xlat16_14.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_16.x = u_xlat16_3.x + (-_EdgeFade);
    u_xlat16_16.x = u_xlat16_16.x + 0.600575984;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_16.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * _AlphaAdjust;
    u_xlat16_16.x = u_xlat16_1.x * 1.58227837 + -0.0500000007;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * 1.58227837;

{

    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_35.x * u_xlat16_43 + u_xlat14;
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_35.x / u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(_RimLightDir, _RimLightDir);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_45 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat0.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_45 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_45;
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat16_45;
    u_xlat16_43 = clamp(u_xlat16_43, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat16_43 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat16_45;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xzw = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_9.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_7.xzw + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_43) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_21) + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = min(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_21) + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_46;
    SV_Target0.w = clamp(SV_Target0.w, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_43 = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlati0 = int(u_xlat16_43);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    for(int u_xlati_loop_1 = 0 ; u_xlati_loop_1<u_xlati0 ; u_xlati_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat28 = float(u_xlati_loop_1);
        u_xlatb42 = u_xlat28<2.0;
        u_xlat16_4.xy = (bool(u_xlatb42)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat5.x = u_xlat28 + -2.0;
        u_xlat28 = (u_xlatb42) ? u_xlat28 : u_xlat5.x;
        u_xlatb28 = u_xlat28<1.0;
        u_xlat16_43 = (u_xlatb28) ? u_xlat16_4.x : u_xlat16_4.y;
        u_xlati28 = int(u_xlat16_43);
        u_xlat5.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPositionDynamicIndex(u_xlati28).xyz;
        u_xlat42 = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
        u_xlat42 = max(u_xlat42, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat47 = inversesqrt(u_xlat42);
        u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat47) * u_xlat5.xyz;
        u_xlat47 = float(1.0) / u_xlat42;
        u_xlat42 = u_xlat42 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati28).x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati28).y;
        u_xlat42 = clamp(u_xlat42, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat42 = u_xlat42 * u_xlat47;
        u_xlat16_43 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDirDynamicIndex(u_xlati28).xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
        u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_43 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati28).z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati28).w;
        u_xlat16_43 = clamp(u_xlat16_43, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat16_43;
        u_xlat42 = u_xlat42 * u_xlat16_43;
        u_xlat16_43 = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_43 = clamp(u_xlat16_43, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_43) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
        u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * _AdditionalLightsColorDynamicIndex(u_xlati28).xyz;
        u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat42) + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD6.yzw * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat5.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlatb42 = _DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978;
    u_xlat16_1.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb42) ? -1.0 : u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat42 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat5.xy = vec2(u_xlat42) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat5.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat5.xy;
    u_xlat10_42 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat5.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(u_xlat16_15.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_1.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat10_42 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (-u_xlat16_1.x) + u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_15.x = log2(u_xlat16_44);
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat16_15.x = exp2(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-u_xlat16_15.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = (-_DigiBaseColor0.xyz) * u_xlat16_15.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_15.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    return;
}

void main()
{

UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _FurLengthTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
float u_xlat18;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.zw = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _NoiseTex_ST.xy + _NoiseTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_FurLengthTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).x;
    u_xlat6.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(_FurLength);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.632000029, 0.632000029, 0.632000029) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = vec2(u_xlat18) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat1.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat18 = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat1.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(_DigiDistore);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * in_TANGENT0.www;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _NoiseTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _FurLengthTex;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
bool u_xlatb0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
bool u_xlatb5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec2 u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_13;
float u_xlat14;
uint u_xlatu14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
mediump float u_xlat16_17;
float u_xlat19;
bool u_xlatb19;
mediump float u_xlat16_20;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_25;
float u_xlat28;
int u_xlati28;
bool u_xlatb28;
mediump float u_xlat16_31;
mediump float u_xlat16_34;
float u_xlat42;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
bool u_xlatb42;
mediump float u_xlat16_43;
mediump float u_xlat16_44;
mediump float u_xlat16_45;
float u_xlat47;
mediump float u_xlat16_48;
mediump float u_xlat16_49;
mediump float u_xlat16_50;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xy = u_xlat16_1.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_43 = dot(vs_TEXCOORD3, vs_TEXCOORD3);
    u_xlat16_43 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_43);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_43) * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_43 = dot(vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz, vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_43 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_43);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_43) * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_43 = dot(vs_TEXCOORD5, vs_TEXCOORD5);
    u_xlat16_43 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_43);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_43) * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyw = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyw;
    u_xlat16_43 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_43 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_43);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_43) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_2.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat16_43 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_43 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_43);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_43) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_43) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_44 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_44 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_44);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_44) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_44 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_44 = min(max(u_xlat16_44, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_44 = clamp(u_xlat16_44, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat42 = texture(_FurLengthTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_5.x = texture(_NoiseTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.zw).x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb19 = !!(0.00999999978>=u_xlat42);
#else
    u_xlatb19 = 0.00999999978>=u_xlat42;
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.x = (u_xlatb19) ? 1.0 : 0.0;
    u_xlat16_17 = (-u_xlat16_5.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_17 + u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_17 = u_xlat16_44 + (-_EdgeFade);
    u_xlat16_17 = u_xlat16_17 + 0.600575984;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_17 * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * _AlphaAdjust;
    u_xlat16_17 = u_xlat16_3.x * 1.58227837;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * 1.58227837 + -0.0500000007;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb5 = !!(u_xlat16_3.x<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb5 = u_xlat16_3.x<0.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb5){discard;}
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_31 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3

SubProgram "gles " {

"// hash: 4e19a9ecca2299c2
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];

uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[20];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _NoiseTex_ST;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.zw = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _NoiseTex_ST.xy + _NoiseTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = u_xlat0;

    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;

    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat16_4.xyz);

    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;

    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = min(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * u_xlat16_18.xxx + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD6.yzw * u_xlat16_22.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat5.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = (-_DigiBaseColor0.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_45) + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_45) * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlatb0 = _DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978;
    u_xlat16_43 = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_43 = (u_xlatb0) ? -1.0 : u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_43 + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16_44 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_44 = min(u_xlat16_44, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_44 * u_xlat16_43 + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat10_0.x = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat10_0.x + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat16_43 = (-u_xlat16_43) + u_xlat16_44;
    u_xlat16_43 = clamp(u_xlat16_43, 0.0, 1.0);
    SV_Target0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_43) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    return;
}

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;

out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;

out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;

float u_xlat18;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.zw = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _NoiseTex_ST.xy + _NoiseTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_FurLengthTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).x;
    u_xlat6.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(_FurLength);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.632000029, 0.632000029, 0.632000029) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = vec2(u_xlat18) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat1.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat18 = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat1.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(_DigiDistore);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;

    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
